31
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:29,360
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto Vladimir Putin ne želi pristati ni na prekid vatre, dakle što je elementarno, dakle ceasefire?

32
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:37,939
